txt.en: With knowledge of Urudanî and her Ghâsh-hai followers, you decide to defeat some of Urudanî's lesser followers in the hopes of loosening her grip upon the prison fortress.
Naerband is located in Talath Úrui.\n\nYou should defeat Urudanî's Ghâsh-hai followers and Flame-spirits within Naerband.
Defeated Urudanî's Warriors and Flame-spirits in Naerband.

The prison fortress of Naerband is populated by vile acts and jailed denizens.
You have successfully defeated many of those who faithfully serve Urudanî, the Flame-wraith.
